author: JOHN COON
title: US beats Canada 2-0 to advance to playoff against Colombia
text:
US beats Canada 2-0 to advance to playoff against Colombia By John Coon , Associated Press | Posted Oct 13th, 2015 @ 7:10pm 0  
SANDY, Utah (AP) — Marc Pelosi and Jordan Kiesewetter scored second-half goals and the United States beat Canada 2-0 on Tuesday to stay alive in CONCACAF qualifying for the Rio Olympics.
